### Body Harmony - Meals API Examples
### Base URL: http://localhost:4000

### 1. Create a new meal
POST http://localhost:4000/meals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Śniadanie",
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "time": "08:30",
  "notes": "Dobre śniadanie przed pracą"
}

### 2. Get all meals for a specific date
GET http://localhost:4000/meals?date=2024-01-15

### 3. Get all meals in date range
GET http://localhost:4000/meals?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-01-31

### 4. Get specific meal with products
GET http://localhost:4000/meals/MEAL_ID_HERE

### 5. Update a meal
PUT http://localhost:4000/meals/MEAL_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Duże śniadanie",
  "time": "09:00",
  "notes": "Zaktualizowane śniadanie"
}

### 6. Add product to meal (creates meal if doesn't exist) - NEW SMART ENDPOINT
POST http://localhost:4000/meals/add-product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mealType": "BREAKFAST",
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "time": "08:00",
  "productId": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
  "quantity": 100,
  "unit": "g",
  "notes": "Good breakfast"
}

### 6b. Add product to meal (traditional way - requires existing meal)
POST http://localhost:4000/meals/MEAL_ID_HERE/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
  "quantity": 100,
  "unit": "g"
}

### 7. Update product in meal
PUT http://localhost:4000/meals/MEAL_ID_HERE/products/MEAL_PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 150,
  "unit": "g"
}

### 8. Remove product from meal
DELETE http://localhost:4000/meals/MEAL_ID_HERE/products/MEAL_PRODUCT_ID_HERE

### 9. Delete a meal
DELETE http://localhost:4000/meals/MEAL_ID_HERE

### 10. Get daily nutrition summary
GET http://localhost:4000/nutrition/daily/2024-01-15

### 11. Get detailed daily nutrition with meals and products
GET http://localhost:4000/nutrition/daily/2024-01-15/detailed

### 12. Get nutrition for date range
GET http://localhost:4000/nutrition/range?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-01-31

### 13. Recalculate daily nutrition
POST http://localhost:4000/nutrition/daily/2024-01-15/recalculate

### 14. Get nutrition statistics for last 30 days
GET http://localhost:4000/nutrition/stats?days=30

### 15. Get nutrition statistics for last 7 days
GET http://localhost:4000/nutrition/stats?days=7

### 16. Health check
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### 17. Get product by EAN (existing endpoint)
GET http://localhost:4000/products/1234567890123

### 18. Get all logs (existing endpoint)
GET http://localhost:4000/logs

